{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef162f9c50","title":"关于检查督促政府各部门向中央报告工作的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"28344cb521","index":0,"year":1950,"month":9,"day":13,"articleId":"ef162f9c50"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"a1a03094a2","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ef162f9c50","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周；指周恩来。"},{"id":"405b7d3123","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ef162f9c50","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长、中央人民政府民族事务委员会主任委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7479ecb2c6","type":"title","text":"关于检查督促政府各部门向中央报告工作的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ef162f9c50"},{"id":"a1a03094a2","type":"paragraph","text":"周：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ef162f9c50"},{"id":"405b7d3123","type":"paragraph","text":"政法系统各部门，除李维汉管的民族事务委员会与中央有接触外，其余各部门，一年之久，千了些什么事，推行的是些什么方针政策，谁也不知道，是何原因，请查询。中财委所属各部门，经过中财委向中央反映，有些是慢一些，但大体是好的；也有若干部门，例如重工业，燃料，农、林、水利等还没有反映。文委系统状况，略同于财委。以上情况，请作一总检查，并加督促。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ef162f9c50"},{"id":"2a467fa2c9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ef162f9c50"},{"id":"4a6eaeef52","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ef162f9c50"}],"page":{"id":"b1e56ccf54","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ef162f9c50","start":154,"end":154}}}},"__N_SSG":true}